# FollowBet — Project Overview

FollowBet is a SvelteKit + TypeScript single-page app where users enter their Instagram handle, the app fetches their real follower count via a server-side proxy, and they gamble it on an animated slot machine.

## Stack

- **Framework:** SvelteKit (full-stack)
- **Language:** TypeScript, strict mode
- **Styling:** CSS custom properties only — no Tailwind
- **Instagram data:** Third-party scraper API, proxied through `src/routes/api/followers/+server.ts`
- **Cache / rate limiting:** Upstash Redis
- **Analytics:** PostHog
- **Hosting:** Vercel (hobby tier)

## Source of Truth

All functional requirements, API contracts, design tokens, analytics events, and out-of-scope items are defined in @REQUIREMENTS.md. Read the relevant section before implementing any feature.

## Key File Locations

- Game state store → `src/lib/stores/game.ts`
- Outcome logic → `src/lib/utils/outcomeEngine.ts`
- Instagram proxy → `src/routes/api/followers/+server.ts`
- Design tokens → `src/app.css`
- Environment template → `.env.example`
